title: Bassnectar Live @ Camp Bisco XII 2013
description:
Bassnectar Live @ Camp Bisco XII July-12-2013

Absolutely incredible set. One of the best if not the best from Bisco XII in my opinion and of many others that were part of this night.
The bass was so intense that the stage sank in the mud! Look up pictures from it, shit was crazy.
